Package: fasola
Title: Access and Query the Sacred Harp Singing Minutes Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jake", "Harmon", email = "jakebharmon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a tidy interface to a SQLite database of Sacred Harp
    (shape-note) singing minutes, including leaders, songs, events, and
    locations scraped from the fasolaminutes parsing pipeline.
